N-1 Testing/Automation: If this is Sprint 2, than in previous sprint 1 we created test plan.
	In this current sprint, we are going to create test plan for the next sprint and execute current sprint
	test plan manually first and automation after which has been created in previous sprint
In-Sprint Testing/Automation: Same sprint test plan will be created and tested manually
	and create automation scripts as well.
	
Hard Assert: Assert.assertEqual(actual,expected);
	- Hard assert will fail the tests and exit out from that steps
Soft Assert: 
	- Soft assert will continue testing if it fails and go execute next other steps as well